Home


I am from Santa Barbara originally and graduated from Santa Barbara High School. I have always enjoyed living here - love the beaches and mountains, great weather, and most especially the Mexican food. I partiularly like the sunsets from Sands beach in the winter.


&lt;img src="images/about1.jpg" alt="Santa Barbara sunset" class="about-img single-img"&gt;




Interests


I love to explore outdoors, from hiking and biking to skiing and swimming - I enjoy it all.


&lt;img src="images/about2.jpg" alt="Hiking adventure" class="about-img double-img"&gt;
